Each a element must contain text or an img with an alt attribute.

A link name allows screen readers to voice what the links does. If there is no link text or the `alt` text is blank, screen readers have nothing to read, so read out the URL instead. To add a name do one of the following:

  • Add text between the a element start and end tags
  • Add an aria-label attribute
  • Add an aria-labelledby attribute
  • Add an img alt attribute if the link contains an img element

1223 <h2>Flooring for Every Room</h2>

1224 <p>From hallways to bedrooms, bathrooms to kitchens, our wide selection of premium flooring materials makes it easy to find the best floor for any room in your house.&nbsp;</p>

1225 <p>We carry many scratch- and water-resistant flooring made from wood, laminate, vinyl, and ceramic tile. Our collection includes flooring rated for high traffic areas and spill-prone spaces like the kitchen or bath. Consider adding personality with a patterned mosaic tile or a rustic hardwood made from reclaimed wood.</p>
